## Lesson content — Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International

The following content is licensed under **CC BY-SA 4.0**:

- All lesson prose, diagrams, quizzes, summaries, and references under
  `src/content/docs/**` except code samples
- Article prose under `src/content/docs/articles/**` when that directory exists
- Planning documents under `Doc/**` and `HANDOVER.md`, `CLAUDE.md`

You are free to:

- **Share** — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format
- **Adapt** — remix, transform, and build upon the material for any purpose,
  including commercial

Under the following terms:

- **Attribution** — you must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the
  license, and indicate if changes were made
- **ShareAlike** — if you remix, transform, or build upon the material, you
  must distribute your contributions under the same license

Full license text: <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode>

